        "host": "127.0.0.1",
        "port": 5000,
        "poll_interval_s": 5.0,
        "recv_timeout_s": 1.0,
        "reconnect_interval_s": 3.0
    },
    "camera": {
        "_comment": "MultiFrame 模式跟盐城对齐。开发机测试时如果手动转编码器跟不上 150 帧节奏，可临时改 acquisition_mode='SingleFrame' + height=15000 + 删 acquisition_frame_count。multiframe_first_wait_s 对齐 Halcon BV_GrapImage:7184",
